Tester

Class rule_extensive_xperiments

  • java.lang.Object
    • Tester.rule_extensive_xperiments

  • public class rule_extensive_xperiments
extends java.lang.Object
    This class allows the experimenter to run numerous experiments at the same time. Two List of String are defined. best_countries lists the numbers of closest countries to the clue from which the cities will be tested. best_cities lists the numbers of most referenced countries from the initial set that will be tested. The tes is done with the Guesser TopXGuesserSsoCountries.

    kemoadrian
